## Our commitment to equity, diversity, and inclusion

Horns of Plenty believe in the power of diversity to build creativity, innovation, and an exciting musical environment. Our commitment to equity, diversity, and inclusion is at the heart of everything we do. We want to build an environment where everyone knows they are valued, respected, and empowered.

Our musical community is made stronger by its diversity. We celebrate these differences and try to increase the representation and voices of all people.
